00:00:28.260 --> 00:00:32.920
the relapse setting, then in the post-transplant consolidation setting, and most recently

00:00:32.920 --> 00:00:36.500
in the frontline treatment for advanced-stage disease.

00:00:37.580 --> 00:00:43.560
So, on the left, the seminal echelon, one trial randomized over 1,300 patients with

00:00:43.560 --> 00:00:49.620
